game_description: Create a detailed jungle in your home using passthrough o 70+ Plants and jungle objects o 60+ Animals o 5+ bonus pieces of furniture Plants, animals, and furniture can be moved, deleted, or respawned (random spawner for each type) Various levels include: - Randomly spawned jungles - Ability to spawn and add plants, animals, and furniture to edit each level - Premade room sizes (10x10 and 30x30 feet) Animals: elephants, tigers, leopards, lions, croc, turtle, dinos, birds, farm animals, and many more
review_1: I am so surprised plants and animals could look this real on my VR. One of my first tries using mixed reality and it has expanded my mind. Def check it out if you want to put plants and animals around your room and see some of this new mixed reality stuff
